import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import IMateria from 'src/app/interfaces/IMateria'; import { PerguntasService } from 'src/app/services/perguntas.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-listar', templateUrl: './listar.component.html', styleUrls: ['./listar.component.css'] }) export class ListarComponent implements OnInit{ materias:IMateria[]=[] constructor(private service:PerguntasService){ } ngOnInit(): void { this.service.consultar().subscribe(dados=>this.materias = dados) console.log(JSON.stringify(this.materias.toString())) } }
